Nagraj

Fictional superhero

Nagraj is a fictional superhero appearing in Indian comic books published by Raj Comics created in the late 1980s by Rajkumar Gupta and his sons Manoj Gupta and Sanjay Gupta. Nagraj first appeared in the comics Nagraj GENL #14 which was written by Parshuram Sharma and illustrated by Pratap Mullick. Wikipedia

Publisher: Raj Comics

Aliases: Green death, Greenman, Nag samrat, Nagraj Shah, Raj, Snake king, Snakeman, Venomous gunpowder

Powers: Agility,  Blast power, Venom breath more.

Parents: King Takshakraj, Queen Lalita
